Package: wlstatus-personal
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libcairo2, libpango-1.0-0, libpangocairo-1.0-0,
 libwayland-client0, libglib2.0-0, libharfbuzz0b,
 libpixman-1-0, libpng16-16, libsystemd0,
 hyprland, waybar, kitty, fish, thunar, kate,
 libfm, bash, zsh, git
Description: wlstatus + personal dotfiles (shell, hyprland, waybar, kitty, fish)
 A lightweight status bar for Hyprland, Sway, and other wlr-layer-shell
 compositors, bundled with personal dotfiles for shell, Hyprland, Waybar,
 Kitty, Fish, and other tools.
 Run 'wlstatus-personal-setup' after install to deploy dotfiles to $HOME.
Maintainer: steven66619 <ste@example.com>
Version: 1.0-1
